			<div class="comment-content "><p>I find this research fascinating. Kudos to you for undertaking it.  I wonder if the Deleuze-Guattari opposition of rhizomatic-arborescent could contribute to the theory behind the historical development you&#8217;re finding.  Also, perhaps one sees a return to the hierarchical model with the &#8220;Tree of Knowledge Systems&#8221; approach of Gregg Henriques.  Thanks for sharing your exciting work</p>
</div>

